title: #92Noon! Burns/Waddle/Zimmer/Leber/Birk
description: Ryan Burns kicks off the show with opinions and intel for tomorrow night's Gophers/Iowa game, then former Bear/current radio host Tom Waddle discusses the Vikings game to finish the first hour. Zimmer's weekly presser gives way to Ben Leber and Matt Birk to wrap the show!
